DirectX

Swap Effect
[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\DirectX\GraphicsSettings]
"SwapEffectUpgradeCache"=dword:00000001
[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\DirectX\UserGpuPreferences]
"DirectXUserGlobalSettings"="SwapEffectUpgradeEnable=1;"


Avalon Graphics


HW Acceleration, Multisample Size, Reference Rasterizer
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Avalon.Graphics]
"DisableHWAcceleration"=dword:00000000
"MaxMultisampleSize"=dword:00000000
"UseReferenceRasterizer"=dword:00000001
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\WOW6432Node\Microsoft\Avalon.Graphics]
"DisableHWAcceleration"=dword:00000000
"MaxMultisampleSize"=dword:00000000
"UseReferenceRasterizer"=dword:00000001
[HKEY_USERS\.DEFAULT\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Avalon.Graphics]
"DisableHWAcceleration"=dword:00000000
"MaxMultisampleSize"=dword:00000000
"UseReferenceRasterizer"=dword:00000001
[-HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Avalon.Graphics]
"DisableHWAcceleration"=dword:00000000
"MaxMultisampleSize"=dword:00000000
"UseReferenceRasterizer"=dword:00000001

Direct3D

VidMemVBs, MMX Fast Path, FlipNoVsync
